title: QuotaChip MouseArea on RowLayout may get zero size; tooltips fail
updated_at: "2026-07-15T04:40:48Z"
---
## Problem
`MouseArea { anchors.fill: parent }` on a `RowLayout` root often gets zero size unless the layout has an explicit width/height; tooltips on chips may never show.

## Location
contents/ui/QuotaChip.qml

## Suggested fix
Use `HoverHandler` on the RowLayout (as PaceBar does) or wrap content in an `Item` with implicit size.

## Source
Review ff0a2eec Issue 22 (nit)